Help Type: command
Command: spinedigest

SpineDigest CLI

Purpose:
  Create and operate portable Wiki Graph archives for AI agents.
  Treat `.sdpub` as the managed archive. Use commands to mutate or inspect it; do not edit archive internals directly.

Object model:
  Search and navigation return URI-addressable objects. Common object kinds are:
    entity, triple, source, summary, chunk

Object commands:
  spinedigest search <archive.sdpub> <query> [--type <entity|triple|source|summary|chunk>] [--chapter <ids>] [--limit <n>] [--cursor <token>] [--json|--jsonl]
  spinedigest get <archive.sdpub> <uri> [--json|--jsonl]
  spinedigest related <archive.sdpub> <uri> [--type <entity|triple|source|summary|chunk>] [--chapter <ids>] [--predicate <text>] [--limit <n>] [--cursor <token>] [--json|--jsonl]
  spinedigest evidence <archive.sdpub> <uri> [--type <entity|triple|source|summary|chunk>] [--chapter <ids>] [--predicate <text>] [--limit <n>] [--cursor <token>] [--json|--jsonl]
  spinedigest pack <archive.sdpub> <uri> [--budget <chars>] [--json|--jsonl]

Archive commands:
  spinedigest create <archive.sdpub> [source] [--input-format <format>] [--llm <json>] [--prompt <text>]
  spinedigest export <archive.sdpub> --output-format <format> [--output <path>]
  spinedigest estimate <archive.sdpub> [--stage <source|graph|summary>] [--json]
  spinedigest index <archive.sdpub> [--json]
  spinedigest transform [--input <path>] [--output <path>] [--input-format <format>] [--output-format <format>] [--digest-dir <path>] [--llm <json>] [--prompt <text>] [--stage <stage>] [--verbose|-v]

Generation queue:
  spinedigest queue add <archive.sdpub> --chapter <id> --task <reading-graph|summary|knowledge-graph> --accept-cost [--boost] [--llm <json>] [--prompt <text>]
  spinedigest queue list [--all] [--active]
  spinedigest queue watch <job-id> [--jsonl] [--from beginning|now]
  Queue generation tasks call an LLM, consume tokens, and may incur provider charges.

Maintenance:
  spinedigest meta <archive.sdpub> [metadata options] [--json] [--llm <json>] [--help|-h]
  spinedigest cover <archive.sdpub> [--llm <json>] [--help|-h]
  spinedigest chapter <action> <archive.sdpub> [options] [--llm <json>] [--help|-h]
  spinedigest config status [--llm <json>] [--help|-h]
  spinedigest help [topic] [--help|-h]

Help contract:
  - Append `--help` to commands and subcommands to see command-specific usage.
  - Use `spinedigest help <topic>` for cross-command concepts, constraints, and runtime behavior.
  - Treat `spinedigest --help` as the root page of the same help system.

